description: This file initializes the React application by rendering the main App component into the DOM element with id 'root'. It imports React, ReactDOM, a CSS file, and the App component. It sets up the rendering within React's StrictMode for development checks.

methods.name: ReactDOM.createRoot
methods.description: Creates a React root for concurrent rendering at the specified DOM node.

methods.name: root.render
methods.description: Renders React elements into the root.
